author: gtully
msg: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-3272 - Handle RejectedExecutionException. In this case avoid the root cause, by allowing the semaphore to limit the enqueue tasks. Issue was in the cancel case locks were being release and the semaphore dropped while the executore queue still had the task pending, it needs to execute before the the samaphore can be released as it gates the task queue
